  <brief_title>A Randomized, Self Controlled Clinical Study of Hemostatic Efficacy of the HemCon Dental Dressing</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Self Controlled Clinical Study of Hemostatic Efficacy of the HemCon Dental Dressing</official_title>
